data.name: Label6.Text
data.value: This application first requires that an additional table, Picture, be added to the Northwind database. Click the button to create this table. If it already exists, it will be dropped and then recreated. If the table is dropped you will lose any data you may have added to it.

data.name: Label2.Text
data.value: Browse for a BITMAP to save to the database. The Open File dialog defaults to the C drive. Sample images can be found in the Graphics\Bitmaps folder installed with Visual Studio .NET (typically C:\Program Files\Microsoft Visual Studio .NET\Common7\Graphics).

data.name: Label5.Text
data.value: The listbox contains all of the images you have saved to the database. To display or delete an image, select the filename and click the appropriate button.
